title: Your all new Stella magazine
text: Make sure to grab the paper this weekend to see your all new Stella magazine, packed with fresh content to engage, entertain and inspire. Highlights include: - More fashion single pages - A new menswear fashion and grooming page with a style columnist - A regular 3-page health and lifestyle feature to follow all diet, fitness and wellbeing trends. - The Stella Beauty Awards â€“ September 27th with 12 categories, one of which will be reader nominated. - 'The Book it List' travel page How to Claim See the newspaper this Sunday for your all new Stella magazine. @telegraph
